{"tid":1539972,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發動今晚十點全城鷗叫 食屎狗林鄭 太遲啦！五大訴求！","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T14:52:32.000Z","uid":311942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f3c578abc2b7c38127096376be3ae7ea41702696","tid":1539972,"uid":311942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:38:12.000Z","msg":"發夢啦你，屌你老母林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n殺左你個仔再同你講聲對唔住你接唔接受丫？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日你接受左林鄭比粒糖你就放棄抗爭嘅朋友？你就係一個好撚自私嘅人！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fbit9cR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffbit9cR.jpg&h=52058892&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由6月9日，林鄭永遠化解危機嘅講話永遠都係三個月先補救<br />\n<br />\n補救？過程我地犧牲左幾多手足？<br />\n我地有幾多手足因爲對香港絕望自殺？<br />\n有幾多手足因爲咁樣盲眼？斷手斷腳<br />\n被狗性侵！羈留室比人搞到無曬尊嚴！<br />\n有手足懷疑被克警亂棍打死！封站一日大清洗當無事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日林鄭講撤回，我地犧牲左足足三個月 由日日上街表達訴求到日日撚狗，<br />\n巴打們日日文宣，有外國人同情我地幫手先可以完成一樣訴求！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日林鄭話比大家知，以前<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">壽終正寢</span>係想哄下你地 暪天過海！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係咪日後我地又都犧牲好多手足先可以撤回好多賣港政策？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醒下啦！香港人，未完架！唔好天真啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上緊法庭嘅手足，為我地犧牲左自己嘅未來，你想袋住先？我即割！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">為左死去嘅手足，繼續五大訴求！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一、全面解散警隊！<br />\n二、根據香港法例第86章成立有法律約束力的獨立調查委員會<br />\n三、收回六一二暴動定性<br />\n四、撤銷對「反送中」抗爭者的無理控罪<br />\n五、落實真普選 必須！非831人大決定！</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今晚鷗叫，再次覺醒！香港人，獅子山精神，我地係可以做到外國朋友都做唔到嘅野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">克警洗定個屎忽等，入去比人吉C眼啦！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共不可怕，我地先係中共同賣港政府最驚嘅敵人！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾日後發動文宣入侵中共！話比支那人知抗爭就有機會，有希望改變未來！<br />\n大話撚中共等支爆啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9021fe9a765b87704b91e8077a0469c117c3551e","tid":1539972,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r54hifk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr54hifk.png&h=4b46846d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xGciM8F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxGciM8F.png&h=54e1b5b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Moqr8G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Moqr8G.jpg&h=25ae8368&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qc9APm2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQc9APm2.jpg&h=111556a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LJZUktH.